Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123227,125021}Mom, do you think Lassie…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125855,127023}It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127023,129734}Although it came from Scotland up to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129734,131027}It has no strength.
