Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151047,152090}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155551,156678}Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158096,160431}Can you carry Lassie home, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175697,177615}And now, here is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184372,186791}Lassie, sleep peacefully…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187625,189752}I won't send you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189752,192088}For this you shall rest assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199011,200430}It's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200430,201139}Yes.
