Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204892,207186}And so, we have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207186,210231}It returned after walking 600 miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210231,211983}It's an unreasonable distance for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:36.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211983,216571}That dog…It returned and it completely\Ndestroyed his hair and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216863,218156}Grandfather!
