Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442755,446092}That dog is a Collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448177,451138}It seems to have happened very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451138,453891}What about that?Can't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453891,457019}No. Are you a journalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457019,460648}Yeah, I'm from the London Journal…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460648,465403}If it is possible to tell us about\Nthe cause of this miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465403,468698}until we publish his command in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468698,469657}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469657,472618}No, it should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:58.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472618,478457}It deserves praise from all people directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481711,484880}I believe that the music\Nyou play draws a xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:10.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484880,490011}up to the fullest of the sky\Nlike the winds of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:14.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490011,494015}So put your hand on your chest and be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494015,497226}Ah, my heart, I'm happy to be lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503399,506110}This is all for this lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506110,508863}It's important not to forget your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518372,519290}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525129,529300}You have walked all this distance\Nand you aren't tired to meet me, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531177,532261}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536140,537641}Oh, sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537641,538434}I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538434,541020}It comes to you in the after noon\Nevery day at the three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541020,542229}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542229,544023}That's right, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544023,548486}No, I just heard about Lassie's story\Nfrom the Duke of Rudling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548486,550571}It's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550571,551155}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551155,553074}You, can you look here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555701,557286}You have to smile again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557286,558579}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559163,560623}It's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560623,562583}It will be a very wonderful story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563000,567588}"The boy who reopened the mine!"And the miracle dog who\Ntraveled a long journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567588,571092}This is why we have to publish\Nthis story in our newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571092,573094}I asked the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573552,575221}No, I can't believe it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575221,579266}Well done, can I talk to you a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579266,580935}What do we do, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582728,583813}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583813,584522}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585356,586524}What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586941,589068}Have you seen the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589068,592530}After work I bought it from\Nthe Jones' store but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593405,595533}I wonder where I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596992,598994}Seriously, my father is weak…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598994,599870}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599870,601372}Is it in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:06.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601372,606544}Yes!You lose the things you always love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606544,607419}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608546,609421}What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611632,614051}Father, in this newspaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614051,615719}I am there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615719,616637}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617346,618389}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618389,620015}John and Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620391,624270}The dog Lassie ​​walked 600 miles to John,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624270,627314}after a long reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627982,628774}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630067,633988}You have become well known in England!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:36.82,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:636824,636824}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668314,670191}Is this from everyone to Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670191,671025}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:17.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671025,677114}After the British newspaper article,\NLassie became very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:22.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677364,682912}I first receivemail of this size at once…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682912,683871}I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683871,684872}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684872,686832}Dad, you came back early today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687708,689585}Ah, I'm tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689585,691754}No, I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692004,693130}Did you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693130,694048}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694048,695716}I don't want another article to be written.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695716,699762}There are many journalists from\Nmultiple companies coming to the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699970,701388}You say Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701388,704642}I think the future of this dog is\Ndifferent from the rest of the dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704642,707645}Oh! Besides, didn't it do something similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707645,709438}As I recall…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:53.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709438,713275}When Dr. Hopper fell in the abyss,\Nit told us to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713275,715110}Ah, tell us more about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715110,716320}Hey Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716320,717988}Don't evade work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717988,720532}I know that, boss…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721200,722868}Are you the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722868,724536}- Uh…\N- We want to talk to you for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725913,727581}Ah… Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727581,729250}Even in your clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729250,730960}And even in the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730960,732002}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732002,735839}I couldn't do anything to the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736215,737925}I was caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:22.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737925,742304}Dr. Hopper told me not to intrude\N"Don't enter the clinic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743555,745057}But what about John?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745057,745641}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745641,748185}He has gone with Priscilla and others to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748185,749228}And also Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749228,750104}Aha…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751647,754108}You see, John? It has become\Na modern newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754108,756277}You've become famous, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756527,758696}I'm not, Lassie is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759238,762533}But when we get to this area,\Nno one will reach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762533,763784}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765619,766578}- Ah!\N- Rock Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,771583}As long as Lassie is in good health,\Nthen we can go up together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771583,772459}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779383,781051}Hey, have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781427,783012}Mr. McNeill…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783846,785014}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785014,789018}What? Actually I'm a journalist,\Nso finding this place is simple for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:14.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789810,794064}In fact, I want to invite you,\NJohn with Lassie to a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:14.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794356,794940}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794940,796400}- A party?\N- A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797526,798485}I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:22.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798485,802406}This is your and your friends\Nsecret rock castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,804575}Can you climb to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804575,807578}Well, can you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807578,808912}I'll take your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808912,810205}No, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810205,811665}I'm busy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811665,813625}Is that right? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813625,816295}It's people's messages to Lassie\Nafter they read the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816712,819798}Instead of Lassie, I will read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820007,820841}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820841,822301}- Who who?\N- Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822926,826180}Isn't it audacious to read\Nthe messages of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826180,828682}Y-yes! I apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829183,831185}He is not our companion as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831185,833562}How long will he stay in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833562,834146}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834146,835439}- Ah!\N- What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835689,837358}T-t-this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837358,839193}Ah…! Wait a moment, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839943,841070}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841070,842905}You feel nostalgic, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843822,844698}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845074,848869}It''s a message from someone\Nwho met Lassie on its journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850913,852790}{\i1}To my dear Purcell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852790,856377}{\i1}No, actually your name is Lassie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856835,859797}{\i1}Dan went out to the village to sell the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859797,862758}{\i1}He brought with him that newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:28.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863592,868722}{\i1}As I expected, you returned after a long wait.{\i1}You also had a precious family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:33.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869056,873727}{\i1}We haven't mistaken to send you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:37.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873727,877189}{\i1}When you returned you were finally happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877189,879274}{\i1}I am also very happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879274,882694}{\i1}Greetings to your precious family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882694,884196}It's a wonderful message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884196,884738}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884738,886365}It's a nice message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886365,890244}Lassie, you met many people on your trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890244,893831}One day I want to thank them with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894748,895624}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895624,899169}Isn't it happy that I wrote\Nabout Lassie in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899169,900587}Eh… Approximately…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900587,902923}If only the concert is held!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902923,904341}These… on what occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904633,906135}Duke Rudling said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:11.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906135,911390}he would organize a concert marking\Nthe miraculous journey of Lassie,and it would be praised there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912015,914852}Of course the villagers will be invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915102,916228}Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916478,919231}Also… can you call
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919231,922234}the old couple at the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922693,923777}What's your reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924445,927865}Of course you can attend the concert together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931201,933370}Ah, as or the concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933370,936957}please keep it secret from\Nthe rest of the journalists!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936957,938709}Our library will work on exclusive coverage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:43.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939418,943964}In the end we couldn't climb the peak…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944339,947301}Although Priscilla had trouble coming here…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962816,967446}Ah! The preparation of the day\Nwas strictly confidential!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967446,969990}This is thanks to John and Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969990,971033}No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971617,974620}Is everything ready, McNeil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974620,976038}Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976747,979416}John and the miners are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979416,982878}I'm sure the equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982878,985297}will appeal to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:30.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986089,990052}Well now I'll look at the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:38.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993472,998477}I'm the one who made the journalists do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998477,1001146}all the hype!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001146,1004191}Because of that I thought of myself only,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004191,1008612}and put John and Lassie under\Nthe pressure of many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008612,1011573}How do I make him trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012741,1014785}Hey hey you have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014785,1017704}How long will you work on our star for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017704,1020457}This child is not nice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020457,1022834}Should I wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022834,1024294}You, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025045,1026922}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026922,1030801}Duke Rudling has invited many\Npeople with high positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030801,1033512}You will become an apprentice\Nif you appear on your nature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033512,1037307}Does my usual look really pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037891,1039560}I didn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039560,1043689}You have a motive so strong that\Nthe mine is not closed because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043689,1046650}No adult can do what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046650,1049653}The Duke of Rudling admire you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049653,1052364}That is why we want to\Nshow you in the finest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052364,1056618}You have to think that this\Nwill  make your future better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056618,1057703}Did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:42.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057703,1062416}You will be treated in this\Nceremony as an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1066712}This clothes will not make you\Njump and play in the fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067462,1068672}So I rely on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068672,1071675}It will change your mindset when\Nit takes you a beautiful picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071675,1072718}Bye…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072718,1074011}Oh! Sir McNeill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074386,1075137}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075137,1076013}Do you still want something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:18:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076263,1080892}Excuse me, will Grandpa Dan\Nand Grandma and Dili really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081101,1082728}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:07.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082728,1087024}Today's concert will highlight the elderly\Ncouple who helped to reunite Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087024,1090277}Well, they seem to be a little late! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090277,1091111}Ah wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091111,1091653}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091903,1093405}Sorry… What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093614,1096033}Rest assured,it will not go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096033,1097576}It is decorated in the next room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097993,1099119}Decorated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099119,1100329}You mean Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100329,1103332}The next is to brush off your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103332,1104291}Eh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104291,1106084}Everything is going well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106084,1107461}Well, just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107461,1109296}These devices will add an amazing effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109296,1111006}We have to pay attention to the guests now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111006,1111798}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111798,1113884}Our sales this time will be better\Nbecause our material is full of tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:34.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113884,1114718}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115594,1117429}Oh, I'm glad to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:41.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117429,1121600}I thought it was a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121600,1123602}Here is the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123602,1125937}All seem to have high positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:49.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125937,1129024}Everyone came because of what they\Nread about Lassie in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129024,1131193}Everyone is excited about John's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:51.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131193,1131860}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132986,1135530}Well you can wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135530,1138575}It took a long time because of your ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138575,1140369}Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141453,1143038}They seem to have started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143038,1145123}When your turn comes I will tell you,\Nwait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145624,1147959}What is this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149628,1152964}Ah, I don't like this shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155258,1157094}We…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157094,1160889}They exaggerated our form, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162015,1163642}In some way, I feel that it is completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:31.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164518,1171066}I'm the only one who found coal,\Nand Lassie faced death on its way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171066,1173527}Yes, that is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177322,1178365}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:44.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178365,1184246}The story of Lassie's long journey\Nwas full of misfortunes and fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184246,1187791}The basis of it was his separation from John
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:54.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187791,1194506}but John…For Greenall Bridge he swore that coal\Nwould come out with all the power he had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194506,1198135}He said: Lassie! Sorry I can't come\Nback to you, with tears in his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198135,1200137}I'll take full responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:05.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200595,1205642}John was very sure he would\Nextract coal for the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205642,1209104}It was here that Lassie decided\Nto return to whatever the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209104,1210564}Now let me introduce to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210564,1215694}Miracle dog Lassie, and its owner John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:16.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216194,1216903}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217237,1218280}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220782,1222033}What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222033,1223493}They have not yet appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225996,1227748}What happened to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228206,1230625}Actually this message…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231585,1234129}Damn, they run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234963,1237132}{\i1}Duke of Rudling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237132,1241136}{\i1}I'm still unable to enter the world of adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241553,1243972}{\i1}I still want to run with Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244264,1247517}{\i1}and the others in the fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247517,1249478}{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249853,1253231}I apologize to everyone, despite the fact\Nthat they have struggled to come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253231,1255108}John Carraclough…
