Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320674,1321842}{\i1}I'm Remy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321842,1323260}{\i1}I sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323260,1325428}{\i1}No, I'm not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325428,1328139}{\i1}Because I have a lot of nice friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328139,1331142}{\i1}But, where is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331142,1332936}{\i1}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333979,1336606}{\i1}"Homeless Girl Remy"\NPlease look forward!
