Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.75,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1357752,1361756}I still remember that time, woo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.75,lassie song en ed,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1361965,1364759}Falling out of the pocket,
